records.addlTxt:
GUILTY plea entered to the charge of retail theft.  Convicted.
Sentence is withheld and the defendant is placed on probation to DOC for twenty-four (24) months.
Conditions of probation:
1) pay $394.93 restitution to Game Stop at 4140 Harbortown Lane,  Manitowoc, WI;
2) complete sixty (60) hours of community service;
3) continue with treatment at Roots Counseling Services;
4) submit to random urines screens and pay for same;
5) maintain absolute sobriety;
6) maintain fulltime employment, schooling or combination;
7) assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
8) provide DNA sample;
9) pay court costs;
10) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
The Court orders expungement under Section 973.015 three years from today's date upon defendant's successful completion of sentence and provided defendant has no major probation violations and complies with all conditions of probation.
Minutes.
